}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== This device is using a '''KeyStream''' (three-chip) chipset (perhaps [http://web.archive.org/web/20080622195108/http://www.keystream.co.jp/en/products/ks2000.php KS2000 + KS2013 + KS2023]).
The '''KeyStream''' logo, "2922PB001-01", a date code of '''0414''', and "Made in Taiwan" is silkscreened on the card in the FCC photos.
The '''Windows''' device description for this card in the FCC manual is "WPC293 Wireless Multimedia Card".
